16:57.469 --> 16:59.203
Hey, Patty.

16:59.271 --> 17:01.905
Sam, thank God you're here.

17:01.974 --> 17:03.473
Hi, Miss Donner. Donner, Donner...

17:03.542 --> 17:05.142
