gonna speak about being a mom

17:33.377 --> 17:35.778
- and having a career.
- Nobody cares.

17:35.846 --> 17:40.349
Please welcome our very own Sam Fox.

17:40.417 --> 17:42.751
Oof.

17:45.489 --> 17:47.923
Yeah, Mom! Go, Mom!

17:56.167 --> 17:59.101
Thank you, Patty.

17:59.170 --> 18:01.670
Um, well...

18:01.739 --> 18:05.641
