because in the end,

18:41.245 --> 18:45.247
the mom, the women,
are the ones left watching.

18:52.189 --> 18:53.722
Okay, this is...

18:56.327 --> 18:59.061
Let me ask you all a question.

18:59.129 --> 19:02.698
How many girls out there
get your period?

19:04.735 --> 19:06.735
Yeah, you heard me.

19:06.804 --> 19:11.139
If anybody here has got their
period yet, put your hand up.

19:11.208 --> 19:12.875
Put your hand up. It's okay.

