19:50.180 --> 19:52.814
Come on, moms, let's hear it for them.

19:52.883 --> 19:57.152
All right, who here has
not gotten their period yet?

19:57.221 --> 19:59.855
Wow! Okay!

19:59.924 --> 20:02.557
Well, you girls are in
for it. You really are.

20:02.626 --> 20:04.593
But we all got your backs, right?

20:04.662 --> 20:08.196
Who here is having
their period right now?

20:08.265 --> 20:10.599
I know I am! Can you tell?

20:10.668 --> 20:12.334
All right! Thank you!

20:12.403 --> 20:15.337
Mrs. Donner! Yeah!

20:15.406 --> 20:18.240
Moms? Thank you! Hands, hands.

20:18.309 --> 20:21.243
Sisters all!

20:21.312 --> 20:26.715
