20:31.221 --> 20:34.122
Mom. Mom.

20:37.194 --> 20:38.727
Thank you!

20:38.796 --> 20:41.663
Thank you for that! Thank you!

20:45.169 --> 20:47.836
Look, we're all girls,
and we're all women.

20:47.905 --> 20:51.073
And we all bleed, and we all suffer.

20:51.141 --> 20:54.643
And then the bleeding stops,
and we still suffer.

20:54.712 --> 20:56.345
But you're gonna find your own path,

20:56.413 --> 20:59.548
