20:59.616 --> 21:01.950
And as long as you believe in yourself,

21:02.019 --> 21:04.553
and you take care of each other

21:04.621 --> 21:06.321
and watch out for each other,

21:06.390 --> 21:08.590
you just make the
rest up as you go along.

21:08.659 --> 21:10.425
That's all there is to it.

21:10.494 --> 21:12.894
That's it! Thank you!

21:12.963 --> 21:15.664
Thank you! Thank you, Detroit!

21:23.941 --> 21:27.175
